dct_title_s: Recens rursus post omnes omnium description urb. Romae topographia
dct_alternative_sm: Recens rvrsvs post omnes omnivm description vrb. Romae topographia
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially and by shading.
Oriented with north toward bottom of sheet.
Author surmised from initials in lower left corner: NB.
Shows plan of Rome, including classical sites, acqueduct ruins, and contemporary city.
